preference.name: PSEAutoViIDPrefix
preference.preference_description: This preference is used on when the preference 'PSEAutoViNewItemPopup' is set to OFF and is used to define an variant item (VI) Id as value of PSEAutoViIDPrefix+auto generated item id. For example, if this preference is set to 'VI' and a item id is auto generated for the VI is 001001 then the VI id will be "VI001001".
